data.description: This stunning home features main floor beautiful wood flooring throughout, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The open concept layout allows for seamless flow between the living room, dining area, and kitchen. The kitchen includes fully equipped modern appliances! Making meal preparation a breeze. Step through the elegant French doors and into the backyard, where you'll find a peaceful oasis perfect for outdoor entertaining or simply relaxing in the fresh air. The spacious master bedroom is truly a retreat, offering ample space for a king-sized bed, a sitting area, and all your furniture needs. Don't miss this amazing opportunity to own this very promising home. Location doesn't get any better, conveniently Located Just minutes from Alamo Ranch, Sea World, Lackland AFB, shopping mall, downtown River Walk and much more! Easy access to most expressways 410, H90, I35. Home is move in ready! If you liked it, then you should of put an offer on it!! Don't let this one slip away! SCHEDULE YOUR SHOWING TODAY !
